<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Canoe Customizations</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/styles.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
        <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
        <script src="/cart.js" defer></script>
    </head>
    <body>
        <header>
            <a href="/"><img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Boaty Shop Logo" class="logo"></a>
            <h1>Canoe Customizations</h1>
            <div class="cart-container">
                <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i>
                <span id="cart-count">0</span>
            </div>
        </header>
        <div class="container container-details">
            <div class="details">
                <h2>Details</h2>
                <p>Our canoe customizations are designed to improve the durability and performance of your canoe. We offer a range of options to suit your needs, whether you're a casual paddler or a seasoned adventurer.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="options">
                <h2>Body Mod Options</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><input type="checkbox" id="kevlar" name="mod" value="Kevlar Reinforcement"> Kevlar Reinforcement - $300</li>
                    <li><input type="checkbox" id="inlays" name="mod" value="Custom Wood Inlays"> Custom Wood Inlays - $500</li>
                    <li><input type="checkbox" id="outriggers" name="mod" value="Stabilizer Outriggers"> Stabilizer Outriggers - $200</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="button-container">
                    <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">Return to Home</a>
                    <a href="/checkout" class="btn">Go to Checkout</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2025 The Boaty Shop</p>
        </footer>
    </body>
</html>
